data.description: SEACREST PINES – ADULT COMMUNITY - 3 YEARS YOUNG AND A CLEAN SLATE! COME SEE THIS CLIFTON MODEL WITH A GENEROUS OPEN FLOOR PLAN AND TWO CAR GARAGE. 2 BED/2 BATH AND OFFICE/FLEX SPACE WITH FRENCH DOORS. KITCHEN FEATURES WHITE CABINETRY WITH GRANITE COUNTERTOPS, ISLAND THAT SEATS FOUR, TILED BACKSPLASH, WALK IN PANTRY WITH CUSTOM DOOR AND SS APPLIANCES. ENJOY THE BENEFITS OF A RAINSOFT RO WATER FILTRATION SYSTEM, INSTANT HOT DISPENSER AND GARBAGE DISPOSAL. AN OPEN AND LARGE DINING/LIVING ROOM AREA INCLUDES COZY GAS FIREPLACE. SUPER SPACIOUS MASTER BEDROOM EN SUITE WITH DOUBLE VANITY, WATER CLOSET, FULL SIZED LINEN CLOSET AND TWO HUGE WALK-IN CLOSETS (ONE MEASURES 12 X 10!). MASTER BEDROOM IS SHOWN WITH TWO QUEEN BEDS! SECOND BEDROOM LOCATED IN FRONT OF HOME AWAY FROM MASTER BEDROOM AND HAS DOUBLE WINDOWS BRINGING IN LOTS OF NATURAL LIGHT. STORAGE SPACE IS NOT A PROBLEM WITH THIS FLOOR PLAN AS IT INCLUDES A LARGE LAUNDRY ROOM AND TWO OVERSIZED HALLWAY CLOSETS. DINING AREA SLIDERS LEAD OUT TO A 18.5 X 9 SCREENED IN PATIO WITH OVERHANG AND A 20 X 20 COMPOSITE DECK WITH RAILS AND GATE. ADDITIONAL HOMEOWNER UPGRADES INCLUDE A PROFESSIONALLY PAINTED INTERIOR, LANDSCAPING WITH PAVERS, CUSTOM WINDOW TRIM AND CORNICES, CEILING FANS, ISLAND PENDANTS AND DIMMER CONTROLS, STORM DOOR, SHUTTERS AND AN ELECTRICAL PANEL TRANSFER SWITCH FOR EASY CONNECTION TO PORTABLE GENERATOR USED TO RUN FULL POWER TO HOME IN TIMES OF POWER OUTAGE. CALL (732) 567-4455
